query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS virustotal_scans (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  scan_type ENUM('file', 'url', 'hash') NOT NULL,
  target_value VARCHAR(500) NOT NULL,
  file_hash VARCHAR(128),
  file_name VARCHAR(255),
  scan_id VARCHAR(255),
  threat_score INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  detections_count INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  total_engines INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  scan_result ENUM('clean', 'suspicious', 'malicious', 'error', 'pending') DEFAULT 'pending' NOT NULL,
  detection_details TEXT,
  scan_metadata TEXT,
  candidate_id INT,
  user_id INT,
  scan_initiated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  scan_completed_at TIMESTAMP NULL,
  created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)
